        title: "How Community-Led Science is Revolutionizing Research",
        author: "Aidan Brown",
        date: "Sep 06, 2025",
        image: "https://static.wixstatic.com/media/11b1c4_37e75f32aa924b718d4eb0309ba0d553~mv2.jpg",
